#
# GOAL: Activate historical topographic maps (Økonomisk Kartverk, Detaljkart Skien, etc.)
#       using GeoID authentication via nib_proxy.php.
#
# FINDINGS:
# 1. WMS Service 'wms.historiskekart' only provides:
#    - 'amt1' (Amtskart) -> WORKS via WMS.
#    - 'georefererte' -> Requires specific map ID.
#    - 'historiskekart' -> Parent layer, not viewable.
#
# 2. Requested layers do NOT exist in WMS:
#    - 'farge_ok' (Økonomisk Kartverk) -> NOT FOUND.
#    - 'his_top_under_50000' -> NOT FOUND.
#    - 'his_top_over_50000' -> NOT FOUND.
#    - 'topo4graatone' -> 500 ERROR on GetCapabilities.
#
# 3. Norge i Bilder implementation:
#    - Uses ArcGIS REST API (not WMS).
#    - URL: services.norgeibilder.no/arcgis/rest/services/ortofoto/ImageServer/exportImage
#    - Authentication: Specialized token, not standard GeoID Basic Auth.
#    - Identification: Uses internal 'nib_project_id' (e.g., 2904) in query.
#
# CONCLUSION:
# The specific historical maps visible on norgeibilder.no are NOT available via
# standard WMS services compatible with Leaflet/OpenLayers without significant
# reverse-engineering of the ArcGIS REST API or specific agreements.
